Package: normalblockr
Type: Package
Title: implementation of the Normal-block model, Gaussian graphical model with latent clustering structure
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jeanne", "Tous", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jeanne.tous@inrae.fr"),
  person("Julien", "Chiquet", role = c("aut"), email = "julien.chiquet@inrae.fr",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3629-3429"))
      )
Description: The Normal-Block model (Tous, J., & Chiquet, J. (2025). An 
             integrated method for clustering and association network inference.
             arXiv preprint arXiv:2503.22467.) can be used to analyse
             multivariate Gaussian data with underlying latent structure. 
             The model infers a structure of statistical dependencies between
             the clusters identified (or given) in the observations.
